\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 217}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's golf bronze medal\", \"from\": 250, \"to\": 279}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"third place\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 352}, {\"ngram\": \"the final round\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After becoming the second Chinese golfer to clinch an Olympic medal following Feng Shanshan at Rio 2016, Lin said she was satisfied with her performance in Paris.\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.6428115712065408, \"rank\": 0.5083897690983166, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 466, \"end\": 479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan_Feng\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Feng Shanshan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan_Feng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan_Feng\"}, {\"begin\": 544, \"end\": 549, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999993022716058, \"rank\": 6.977288569903371e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio 2016\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 493, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel quite amazing.\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I had a chance today, but I know it's going to be a very tough battle,\\\" Lin told CGTN Sports Scene's Jiang Mengxi.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 663, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.38496908821173e-22, \"text\": \"CGTN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Global_Television_Network\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 596}, {\"ngram\": \"a very tough battle\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 651}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 657}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I did not have the best start I am asking for.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 748, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best start\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 731}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am very proud of myself the way I fought back at the end.\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's good enough to win a medal and that's even better.\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I am very overwhelming right now.\\\"\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lin climbed four places over the last 18 holes and said her secret was staying consistent despite a slow start.\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"four places\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 18 holes\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"her secret\", \"from\": 963, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"a slow start\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was a little disappointed when I see so far back,\\\" Lin said.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But then I said to myself, I have been playing very consistent this week and I think at the back nine, the consistency is going to be a very good weapon.\", \"from\": 1084, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the consistency\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"a very good weapon\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I just need to keep doing what I have been doing.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And, and also I stopped looking at the scoreboard.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scoreboard\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I just wanted to play my own golf.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my own golf\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a good game plan, and then I executed it really well and then it ended up good enough to give me a medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good game plan\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also revealed that she learned a lot from Feng and said the two had a memorable conversation before Lin departed for Paris.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999993022716058, \"rank\": 6.977288569903371e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"Feng\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"a memorable conversation\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1589}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I get to talk to Shanshan right before I leave for Paris,\\\" Lin said.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan\", \"score\": 0.9992143901078622, \"rank\": 0.0007862275603778881, \"text\": \"Shanshan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanshan\"}, {\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999993022716058, \"rank\": 6.977288569903371e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was explaining my anxiety and I was like, 'I do not know what to what to expect here.'\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1781, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my anxiety\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then she just asked me one question: if this is your third Olympic or your last Olympics, what kind of finish you think you will be satisfied with yourself.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one question\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"your third Olympic\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"your last Olympics\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"finish\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1895}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I thought about it and I said, 'well, medal, of course.'\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then she said, well, then that's the goal.\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have nothing to lose.\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have to keep grinding out.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing's going to be in the way when I am fully focused on this target and then I think that was a really important conversation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nothing\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"this target\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"a really important conversation\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2246}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLOAD\", \"from\": 2255, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation report hotline\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"010-85061466 SITEMAP\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"OUR APP\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2402}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2445}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation report hotline\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2476}]}]}"